name: Recollection of a Meal - NUGGY N' FRIES SET #1
description: Historical Log of Apocalyptic Events Near You is proud to enchant your visual senses with: A reminder of the ease in which our carnal desires can be quenched by the power of poultry bits! Bathed and rolled up with care in a soft mixture of quail egg and powdered toast, then made to suffer in the heat of a thousand olive souls, this abundant meat is cooked to perfection and set to be partners in crime with a similarly massive portion of potato fries! Lascivious eyes will forever be doomed to only be allowed to stare, as you parade your trophy amongst the masses of hungry folk!
